snippet.title: Midgard - Against the midway boss I guess
snippet.description:
Midgard is considered kusoge, and I've been playing it. I think I've made some progress! And finally it took me out of the same kind of dungeons. To a black place with a dumb dragon, then to another dungeon.

I was going to record the full playthrough, but I forgot.

For more information about this game, see this:
http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/midgard/
